==THE AXIS OF EVIL IS OUT THERE==
The list of the Axis of Evil contains people that doesn't agree with him, that have disliked him, that have befriended him, or that have not given in to what his needs are.  The term "[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Axis_of_Evil Axis of evil]" was used by George Bush in his State of the Union Speech to describe regimes that he accused of sponsoring terrorism and seeking weapons of mass destruction.  So the term "Axis of Evil" was not his orginial idea.  He used the term in early 2003 or early 2004 to describe the group of people that he BELIEVE has been "Conspiring" against him.  It appears as everything bad that happens to him is a conspiracy and it's all the "Axis of Evil" doing.  And each year he seems to keep adding more people to his list of the "Axis of Evil."  Some people that finds out they are apart of that list don't understand why they are on it.  Especially when they never seem to have contacted or know of the Cardinal King (Matthew Abernathy) in their life.

